```{r pancreas 32320048, include=FALSE}

PMID_32320048 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32320048', database = 'PubMed')

PubMed_32320048 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32320048$eprint)

doi_32320048 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32320048$doi)

Sys.sleep(1)

```
